elements firstterm firstterm Element
firstterm &firstterm.purpose;
&firstterm.synopsis.gen; Description
This element marks the first occurrence of a word or term in a given context.
Processing expectations
&format.inline; FirstTerms are often given special typographic treatment, such as italics.
&firstterm.parents.gen; &firstterm.children.gen;
Attributes
linkend
Linkend points to a related element, perhaps the Glossary definition of the term.
See Also &firstterm.seealso.gen;
Examples
